@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_vgonca(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = (wp.abs(wp.abs(v1 + 0.81)) + ((v0 + 0.54 - tmp + 0.68) - tmp))
    v1 = 0.72
    v0 = (wp.abs(tmp) - v0)
    v1 = (wp.sin((v0 + 0.82 + tmp + 0.89)) * (tmp + wp.abs(tmp + 0.65)))
    v2 = (wp.sin(0.97) + (wp.abs(v1 + 0.82) + (v1 + 0.10 - v0 + 0.11)))
    data[tid] = v0
